<h3>Play Masterloo!</h3>
<p>A exciting 4-player card game: Draw 3 cards from a shuffled standard 52-card deck, place them in slots 1-3, and compete in high-card duels. Matchmake with others, chat during games, and aim for the top of the leaderboards!</p>
<p>Prizes: Active players may occasionally receive fun rewards like badges or profile highlights. Donations via CashApp enter you into special prize draws for extras like custom icons.</p>
